  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/EXqWHENKeJA?si=tI2wvUsy4bIADzFJ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To activate your Commerce product, Administrators should navigate to the Product Activation tab on the sidebar navigation&nbsp; in <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0041be; text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;\" target=\"_blank\">Customer Portal</a> and select </span><strong>Commerce.</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Liferay Version 7.3 - 7.4</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For Commerce on Liferay Versions 7.3 -7.4, your Commerce Activation Page will display the following chart giving you instructions on how to activate your Commerce Product.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"cp_commerce.PNG\" src=\"https://support.liferay.com/documents/d/customer-portal/22911157464077\"></p>\n\n<p><strong>Liferay Version 7.1 - 7.2</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For Commerce on Liferay Versions 7.1 -7.2, you can download pre-generated licenses for each subscription term.&nbsp; If you have multiple subscription terms active, you’ll be able to select and download a license for each one.&nbsp;</span></p>"
      },
